cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper involves the use of deep learning to denoise images, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also involves the design and training of a custom deep learning network, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the use of metrics to assess the performance of the algorithm falls under neural networks (cs.NE) and multimedia (cs.MM).
